Text: Let me start by saying this is a straight-up good guys vs. bad guys, shoot 'em up action movie. Would you expect anything less from Ahhnold? I'll say that I was happy to hear Arnold was returning to the big screen for starring roles once his Governorship was over. Quality was so-so but there is a HD one at stand.blake7.net which worked great for me. Enjoy this entertaining movie!
